WEBVTT

00:08:27.823 --> 00:08:30.356
"I will never be able to talk
about Chinese philosophy

00:08:30.380 --> 00:08:31.784
in front of a huge audience."

00:08:31.808 --> 00:08:32.856
(Laughter)

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.355
Or we can just open up and enjoy the ride.

00:08:35.828 --> 00:08:38.099
It can only be an amazing experience.

00:08:39.077 --> 00:08:42.119
So humility, harmony and openness.

00:08:42.703 --> 00:08:46.308
Those are the three lessons I learned
from the philosophy of water so far.

00:08:46.752 --> 00:08:49.324
They nicely abbreviate to H-H-O,

00:08:49.348 --> 00:08:50.518
or H2O.

00:08:50.542 --> 00:08:51.605
(Laughter)

00:08:51.629 --> 00:08:54.876
And they have become
my guiding principles in life.

00:08:55.885 --> 00:08:58.505
So nowadays, whenever I feel stressed,

00:08:58.529 --> 00:09:02.001
unfulfilled, anxious
or just not sure what to do,